ned for safety hazards by way of a Process Hazard Analysis (PHA).  The PHA of the refrigeration system consisted of the following:



(1)    Hazard and Operability (HAZOP) study;

(2)    Facility Inspection;

(3)    seismic assessment; and

(4)    series of safety checklists.



The PHA study generated a list of recommendations for improving safety at the facility, all of which have been verified as complete.
